  "time_ut": 1660451843,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Childish news about Nallur Utsavam",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna gives untrue and childish comments to the media about the Nallur temple festival. Jaffna regarding Deputy Chief Minister Tu. Eesan. Varadarajan Parthiban, member of the municipal council, condemned the council.",
        "Jaffna. The member of the municipal council said this while the monthly session of the municipal council was held. In addition,",
        "The historical background of Nallur Kandaswamy Temple and Jaffna Municipal Council is very long. Whether we are where we are today or where we will be in the future, everything is blessed by Nallur Kandan.",
        "This High Council is working with the scepter blessed by Nallur Kandan for the work that the Jaffna Metropolitan Council has been doing for the Lord Nallur Kantha for years. It is not advisable for us to act in such a way as to affect that historical bond.",
        "Arnold was the mayor in 2020. As he traveled abroad during Nallur Perundruvizha, Deputy Chief Minister Dhu Eesan held the position of Deputy Chief Minister of the city. At that time (year 2020) he had held a media conference regarding the Nallur Kandaswamy temple festival.",
        "In that media meeting, due to the corona virus, the supporters could not do any formalities, including the Kavadis. He had said that he could not give alms. He has re-shared the video of the 2020 Nadathiya press conference through his homepage this time during the Nallur festival. By this he creates a confusion among the people.",
        "Apart from that, the Deputy Chief Minister who commented to a media 3 days ago, when I was acting Chief Minister in 2020, when there was a question whether the Nallur Kandan temple festival would be held or not due to the corona virus, the Presidential Secretariat sent letters to the Ministry of Health and other levels and increased the permission for only 50 people to participate in the festival. He had irresponsibly made untrue comments to the media.",
        "He also expressed his views that the present Chief Minister has not taken any effort to come up with the Nallai Kandan outer road in 2021.",
        "What is the connection between Nallur Kantha Peruman coming out and the mayor? It is ridiculous that the Deputy Chief Minister of a city acts without even that understanding.",
        "He has childishly informed the media that the present Chief Minister has not taken any effort to hold the 2021 festival as if the 2020 festival was done by him.",
        "Nallur Kandaswamy temple is not only a symbol of Saiva Tamil people but it is seen as a symbol of Jaffna by all. He said that it is a historical divine work, so if he has any interest in that work, he condemns such childish comments to the media and requests him to behave responsibly. (R)"
      ],
